{"tid":873910,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"占美華迪比賽中途去屙屎","createTime":"2018-10-23T19:50:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T19:50:31.000Z","uid":99568,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6275dae34dfa62e3dc07e3db317f77fa90d1c230","tid":873910,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T19:50:12.000Z","msg":"今晨(周二)英超李斯特城作客1比3不敵阿仙奴，比賽尾聲發生一幕奇怪畫面，李斯特城王牌前鋒占美華迪喺比賽進行期間，突然向領隊佩爾示意要離場，隨即急急腳走奔更衣室，而且跑出去嗰陣動作極唔自然，完全係一副「急屎樣」。當時已經係賽事第87分鐘，由於李斯特城已經用晒3個換人名額，所以華Dee離場後球隊只能10人應戰，而占美華迪最終亦冇出返球場。 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7ca0aa6656aca1f387f07c62e690611e6439ca7","tid":873910,"uid":99568,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T19:50:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}